9 An Act relating to professions and occupations;
amending 59 O.S. 2021, Section 698.2, which relates
10 to veterinary profession definitions; modifying
certain definitions; defining terms; amending 59 O.S.
11 2021, Section 698.12, which relates to allowable
conduct; providing fee structure for Pulsed
12 Electromagnetic Field Therapy; establishing Pulsed
Electromagnetic Field Therapy certification;
13 providing for codification; and providing an
effective date.
